title: Ali Al-Baluchi
text: Ali Al-Baluchi (born 6 April 1959) is a Kuwaiti <a href="boxing">boxer</a>. He competed in the <a href="Boxing%20at%20the%201988%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Super%20heavyweight">men's super heavyweight</a> event at the <a href="1988%20Summer%20Olympics">1988 Summer Olympics</a>.
